<HEADLINE> Libya Desires for Foreign Investments </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, February 19 (Xinhua) -- Libya said it desires for
foreign investments and said that it will provide privileges and
incentives for investors, Tunisian media reported Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Libya will do its best to encourage foreign investments,
visiting Secretary of Planning of Libya's General People's
Committee (Cabinet) Gadallah Azouz Al-Talhi told the press here.
</P>
