support of respected leaders of the opposition, not disgruntled
politicians who switch parties because they were not given slots
in the campaign ticket," he said.
</P>
<P>
He also shrugged off reports that at least 24 members of the
House of Representatives are defecting to the opposition, saying
an overwhelming majority of the congressmen from the ruling party
have pledged to support the Lakas-NUCD ticket.
</P>
