<HEADLINE> Laudrup to Move to Chelsea </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, February 19 (Xinhua) -- Danish winger Brian Laudrup was
set to sigh for Chelsea after his contract with Scottish club
Rangers expired at the end of the season, newspapers in England
and Denmark reported Thursday.
</P>
<P>
