<P>
Samax is in a position to plan a full feasibility study with a
continued exploration program, the newspaper said.
</P>
<P>
Tanzania, which has abundant gold resources, has implemented
favorable policies in handling approval procedures and taxation
for investors in the mining sector over the past decade. A number
of investors have been licensed to develop mineral resources in
the country.
</P>
<P>
