settle the crisis over Iraq's stand on international inspections
aimed at preventing its development of weapons of mass
destruction. Both countries have expressed grave concern over the
increasing tensions in the region and have said that diplomatic
action was the only way out.
</P>
<P>
The Indian Express:
</P>
<P>
-- The polls in Coimbatore have been postponed by six days and
will now be held on February 28 because of a string of bomb
explosions since February 14. 
</P>
