Maritime Union of Australia and canceling its industrial awards if
the union takes national action over the waterfront dispute.
</P>
<P>
The Australian Financial Review:
</P>
<P>
-- Growing Federal Government fears that Indonesia is nearing
economic and political chaos became public Wednesday, with strong
warning from Australia's top military commander and senior
ministers about the threat posed to regional stability. 
